# Visual_Studio_Useful_Extension

The following list is for visual studio 2019

## Vim
VsVim: vim simulater for visual studio
Relative Number: show relative line number at side bar

## Refactor & Analyzer
Roslynator 2019 - a collection of hundreds of analyzers and refactors

## Unit Test
NUnit 3 Test Adapter
Test Generator NUnit extension - create unit test for NUnit 3 framework

## Code Formater
Format document on Save - auto formating the files when saved
Code Alignment - help you present code beutifully
Trailing WhiteSpace Visualizer - show trailing whitespaces and you can remove the trailing spaces as you need

## Other Useful Tool
CodeMaid - find file in solution explorer
Auto Save File - save files every 5 seconds
Toggle Comment - comment and uncomment of selected lines of code
Visual Studio Spell Checker (VS2017 and Later) - check spelling
